snippet.title: Why is Negative times Positive Negative? (TANTON Mathematics)
snippet.description:
This is a subtle question! 

In this video I make clear which piece of mathematics we choose to accept (and it is a choice!) that makes numbers behave this way. If you choose not to make this choice, that's fine! You'll have created for yourself a new type of mathematics.
